PRODUCT DESCRIPTION: This is a Highly Successful Retail Weighing scale with a solid rugged body and excellent quality and accuracy. This device can be used to weigh upto 30kg with a triple accuracy of 1g,2g & 5g. This scale comes with two bright red attractive displays one in front and one on the Pole(for customers view). This scale is made of ABS VIRGIN PLASTIC outer body and provided with a dust cover free. The big pan size of 400x350x120mm makes it an ideal choice for all retail shops. Its an ideal choice for all Retail stores, Kirana, Grocery, Supermarkets, Meatshops, Bakeries and Sweet shops.
